sentence.text: In this study, we used quantitative proteomic analyses to compare a highly metastatic cancer cell line and a parental breast cancer cell line; and observed that mitochondrial respiratory chain complex I assembly, an accessory subunit of the mitochondrial membrane respiratory chain NADH dehydrogenase (complex I), was down-regulated in highly metastatic breast cancer cells.

entity.text: mitochondrial respiratory chain complex I assembly
